"Empowering Growth, Inspiring Success – Your Business Hub Awaits!"

AMAR BUSINESS PARK

Developed by Amar builders- Amar Business Park is a Grade A asset in the SBD (Baner MicroMarket) of Pune. In a close proximity of hotels such as the Orchid hotel, it is a multi-tenanted project with occupiers present from diverse sectors. The project is a mix of retail and commercial space and provides varied amenities to the tenants.

With our preserved historical significance and prestigious location, Amar Business Park offers a classic and luxurious Financial District apartment rental experience. Contact us today for more information about making Amar Business Park your next Office.

Project Information

  • Project : Amar Business Park Baner
  • Price : 2.20 Lac – 16 lac
  • Area : 2000 Sq.Ft. – 20000 Sq.Ft.
  • Project Area : 599999.00 Sq.Ft
  • Possession : Immediately
  • City : Pune
  • Location : Baner
  • Commencement Certificate : Yes
  • Occupancy Certificate : Yes
  • Approved By : RERA
